setup=_=>{createCanvas(W=800,W,WEBGL)
R=random
g=createGraphics(W,W).textFont`Monaco`.textSize(32)
g.drawingContext.filter=`drop-shadow(0 0 9px#0ff)`
for(i=81;i--;)g.fill(0,R(81,255),W).text(R([0,1]),i%9*89+44,~~(i/9)*89+44)
background(0)
texture(g)
box(520)}//#„Å§„Å∂„ÇÑ„ÅçProcessing https://t.co/BWzmpEaFr0
